- `docs/adr/001-name-sanitization.md` — Name sanitization
- `docs/adr/002-services-layer.md` — Services layer between routes and DB
- `docs/adr/003-zod-as-ssot.md` — Zod schemas as SSOT
- `docs/adr/004-soft-delete.md` — Soft-delete pattern
- `docs/adr/005-dual-auth.md` — Dual auth (session + Bearer API key)
- `docs/adr/006-proxy-auth-middleware.md` — Custom proxy instead of Next.js middleware
- `docs/adr/007-jsonb-engine-storage.md` — Engine state as single JSONB column
- `docs/adr/008-id-internal-name-external.md` — Internal IDs, external names
- `docs/adr/009-decimal-precision.md` — Decimal.js for arbitrary-precision arithmetic
